\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">用自家遊戲殺死晒第三方廠商</span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n自己啲game吸引唔到人都可以瀨人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nGoodest logic</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個係事實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nSony 同 MS 會盡量 同其他廠夾好時間，避免太多大作 同時出 ，會自己人打自己人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n任天堂見有其他作品上市，就故意改期同人撞，大家搶黃金檔期咪兩敗俱傷囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以攪到其他game廠怕咗佢，於是冇人幫佢出game,得返SEGA同佢關係好少少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以任天堂只能靠自家作品救命<br />\n任天堂已經風光不再"},{"pid":"76c930cea6946353baa76a5e00ad29eb28ee3d93","tid":12483,"uid":25825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T17:26:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>任天堂有創意好多喎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n食老本公司，係近年彈起左一隻splatoon 就叫最有創意？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁比起萬年車槍既Sony同萬年初音人龍又的確係有創意好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n任天堂幾時肯出全新IP既game呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a348ca3bf80351d6889e958bae4788f33f1ba59f","tid":12483,"uid":25825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T17:29:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>任天堂有創意好多喎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n食老本公司，係近年彈起左一隻splatoon 就叫最有創意？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁比起萬年車槍既Sony同萬年初音人龍又的確係有創意好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n任天堂幾時肯出全新IP既game呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nXbox都多新IP過任天堂"},{"pid":"b971c29b3655d438b7126a64d4db77786177b12d","tid":12483,"uid":25825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T17:34:16.000Z","